A mod for Project Zomboid which will create a listening ring around the player.

Installation:
1. Press 'Zip', just below the repository description.
2. Extract this archive inside the root dictionary of Project Zomboid.
3. Start game
4. ??
5. Profit

Usage:
When in-game, hold 'L' to view listening circle.
The size of the 'smudge' depends on the range of the sound and your distance to it.
The transparency is affected by the volume.